---
---
<section id="pedir" class="py-20 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12 relative overflow-hidden">

  <!-- Fondo degradado naranja/mango -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF8F00 0%, #FFC107 45%, #FFD54F 100%);"></div>

  <!-- Decorative fruit circles -->
  <div class="absolute top-[-60px] right-[-60px] w-[280px] h-[280px] rounded-full bg-white/8 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-[-80px] left-[5%] w-[220px] h-[220px] rounded-full bg-white/6 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-[20%] left-[40%] w-[120px] h-[120px] rounded-full bg-white/5 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-[760px] mx-auto text-center">

    <p class="font-body text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-white/70 mb-5 reveal">
      Empieza hoy
    </p>

    <h2
      class="font-display font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-5 reveal reveal-delay-1"
      style="font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 68px); text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);"
    >
      Tu primera caja de fruta,<br class="hidden md:block"/> recogida esta mañana.
    </h2>

    <p class="font-body text-[17px] text-white/80 leading-[1.65] mb-12 max-w-[520px] mx-auto reveal reveal-delay-2">
      Dinos dónde entregamos y recibirás fruta de temporada directamente del huerto, sin compromisos.
    </p>

    <!-- Form -->
    <form
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-[520px] mx-auto reveal reveal-delay-3"
      onsubmit="return false;"
      novalidate
    >
      <input
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="Tu correo electrónico"
        required
        autocomplete="email"
        class="flex-1 field text-[15px]"
        style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);"
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="btn-leaf shrink-0 text-[15px] px-7 py-3"
        style="background: var(--color-leaf); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(27,94,32,0.35);"
      >
        Pedir ahora
      </button>
    </form>

    <p class="mt-5 font-body text-[12px] text-white/55 reveal reveal-delay-4">
      Sin permanencias · Cancela cuando quieras · Primer pedido sin compromiso
    </p>

  </div>
</section>
